cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.DS, cs.NE. 

The paper deals with a machine learning problem related to class imbalance and concept drift in online learning. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.CV (Computer Vision) as these categories are closely related to machine learning. The paper also involves data streams, which suggests cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) as a possible category. Finally, the use of resampling techniques suggests cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) as another possible category.
